;===============================================================================
;◆イベント◆

; 初期発生イベント
events = [2, 3, 4]

;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*event_1
;[exp] WAY == "e"

@delevent
@wait time=500
[texton]
[リーダー f=05]「That's...!」[k]
On the cliff opposite, something small can be seen emitting a magical light.[k]
The unique glow of a magic stone. No doubt about it, that's the Opal Magic Stone.[k]
[if exp='game.isFreeMode']
	The previous owner dropped the magic stone in an inconvenient place. It will be extremely difficult to retrieve it.[k]
	It seems impossible to get there from this cliff. I'll have to ask a girl to get it from the women's bath.[k]
[else]
	The previous owner dropped the magic stone in an inconvenient place... It will be extremely difficult to retrieve it...[k]
	It seems impossible to get there from this cliff. I'll have to ask a girl to get it from the women's bath.[k]
[endif]
[textoff]

[eventoff]
;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*event_2
;[exp] true

@delevent
@delevent num=1
@delevent num=4
@delevent name=山小屋パブ num=1
@delevent name=山小屋パブ num=2
@changefloor pimg=void
@getitem item=オパールの魔石
@wait time=500
[texton]
[if exp='ELF || SYL'][キャラ f=09]「Good, I got the magic stone. But how am I supposed to get back...?」[k]
[elsif exp='HUM || DWA || GNO'][キャラ f=09]「It's great that I got the magic stone, but now how do I get back...?」[k]
[endif]
The path back to the bathhouse was a steeper cliff than I had expected, and it seemed impossible to climb up.[k]
[if exp='ELF || SYL'][キャラ f=06]「Well then, we'll just have to find a way back...」[k]
[elsif exp='HUM || DWA || GNO'][キャラ f=06]「I guess we'll have to find a way back, somehow...」[k]
[endif]
[textoff]

[eventoff]
;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*event_3
;[exp] true

; バスタオルを持ち込む方法はあるのでその対策
@delevent
@eval exp='tf.temp = game.party.findItem(o.バスタオル)'
[eventoff cond='tf.temp === void']
@eval exp='game.curChara = tf.temp.chara'
@eval exp='while(game.party.ejectItem(o.バスタオル))'
[texton]
[キャラ f=25]「Oh, the bath towels...!」[k]
We suddenly noticed all the bath towels were gone.[k]
Apparently, when climbing down here, they got caught on a tree branch on the cliff.[k]
[textoff]

[eventoff]
;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*event_4
;[exp] game.findItem(o.オパールの魔石) === void

; バスタオルを持ち込む方法はあるのでその対策
[texton]
[if exp='HUM || DWA || GNO'][キャラ f=05]「Um, shouldn't we search this place a little more thoroughly?」[k]
[elsif exp='ELF || SYL'][キャラ f=05]「Hey, shouldn't we search this place properly?」[k]
[endif]
[textoff]
@walk move=w

[eventoff]
;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
